{"tid":2262087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院再出招 列中國統促會為外國代表機構","createTime":"2020-10-28T21:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T07:11:41.000Z","uid":337052,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"01059019434d453b6c6801c1355852f68094a5a0","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T21:59:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美國務院再出招 列中國統促會為外國代表機構</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/10/29 04:52<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者徐薇婷華盛頓28日專電）<span class=\"red\">美國國務卿蓬佩奧今天表示，中共將總部位於美國華府的「中國和平統一促進會」當成掩護機構，在美國進行外宣與惡意影響力行動，國務院決定將促進會列為外國代表機構。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）今天發聲明指出，中國和平統一促進會（National Association for China&rsquo;s Peaceful Unification，以下簡稱華府統促會）受到中共中央委員會統一戰線工作部（統戰部）控制，而統戰部功能是替中共消除威脅，並在海外擴展影響力及進行外宣。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示，<span class=\"red\">國務院依據外國代表機構法（Foreign Missions Act），將華府統促會列為外國代表機構；目的與8月將孔子學院美國中心（Confucius Institute U.S. Center）列為外國代表機構相同，都是要讓外界了解這些組織性質，並認清他們傳播的訊息來自北京。</span><br />\n<br />\n孔子學院美國中心主責管理美國國內孔子學院。蓬佩奧8月時指出，該中心在美國校園推動中國外宣及惡意影響力行動，孔子學院則是中共資助成立的全球影響力、文宣工具。<br />\n<br />\n根據華府統促會網站，該團體是由旅居美國大華盛頓地區的華人與華僑組成，「旨為堅持『一個中國』的原則，反對分裂中國國土和主權的一切言行」，並負責「研究中國統一可行方案，為中國的最終完全統一努力」。<br />\n<br />\n依據外國代表機構法規定，未來華府統促會必須向美方提供雇員名單及註冊現有房產，購買或租賃新房產前也須事先獲得批准。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧指出，除了華府統促會外，統戰部在美國還有其他協助散播北京惡意影響力的附屬組織；美方決定終止2011年1月19日為了促進地方合作，與中國簽署建立「美中省州長論壇」的備忘錄。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示，備忘錄簽署後，總部位於北京的「中國人民對外友好協會」試圖直接惡意影響美國州層級與其他地方領袖，以推動中共全球計畫。協會行徑有損論壇最初的立意良善。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，人與人真實交流有助不同文化建立理解，但統戰部並非人與人交流的媒介，反而是把華府統促會等團體當成「掩護組織」，推動中國外宣與惡意影響力行動。（編輯：楊昭彥）1091029<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202010290013.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202010290013.aspx&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KivlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=1d826c9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202010290013.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"4c83f63a7e01ac65a1315521553ef4e37cc3dfe9","tid":2262087,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T21:59:50.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc81aa8c05cf270174ad427db5588a4fc4e6a0c4","tid":2262087,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:01:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">大和田立即坐返低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2f99441a3da05a6b7667c86c1b1df9865083bf6a","tid":2262087,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cb5bdcdbb9a2f32d91452ed87b65ba97fbe72f","tid":2262087,"uid":239336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAJVAo4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAJVAo4.gif&h=f4df247b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3584afbe3d4e3b2beffa4cbb64f288e0fd4391b2","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc81aa8c05cf270174ad427db5588a4fc4e6a0c4","tid":2262087,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:01:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">大和田立即坐返低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiUEX6S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiUEX6S.gif&h=23f74a11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75fa2060f0c684e5a8c385b0d604c9330da7603a","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c83f63a7e01ac65a1315521553ef4e37cc3dfe9","tid":2262087,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T21:59:50.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Facethe87truth/videos/300148970634549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFacethe87truth%2Fvideos%2F300148970634549&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KivlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=ce7496bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Facethe87truth/videos/300148970634549</a><br />\n統一促進黨主席張安樂踏進棺材"},{"pid":"4e580068815e3dd1770a41ff16adccee58f4fdf6","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"澳門地區中國和平統一促進會舉辦紀念台灣光復75週年座談會<br />\n时间：2020年10月27日 09:11  稿件来源：中國新聞社"},{"pid":"892d6ddb4ad774239cd05cf2e8ff581fa6a39c7c","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">中國和平統一促進會香港總會會長姚志勝</span>表示，「十三五」時期，中央带領全國各族人民開拓創新、砥礪前行，加快經濟結構調整步伐，積極應對風險挑戰，實現經濟持續穩定增長和人民生活水平不斷提高。「期間，國家經濟增速始終居於世界主要經濟體的前列，一系列重大科技成果相繼問世，發展協調性更好、持續性更強，民生保障更有力，並為全球經濟增長注入巨大動力。」"},{"pid":"7f30a8f320824bec68266758dd048bd982b250df","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:23:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美國務院將中國和平統一促進會列為外國使團</span></strong><br />\n2020-10-28電郵評論Share打印<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">美國國務卿蓬佩奧10月28日發表聲明，將美國華盛頓中國和平統一促進會（NACPU）列為外國使團。</span><br />\n<br />\n聲明說，中國統戰部門（UFWD）是中國共產黨（CCP）的機構，其任務是消除對該黨統治的威脅，並將其影響力傳播到海外。中共將此黨派機構視為推進北京政策的&ldquo;法寶&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n如今，美國國務院根據美國《外國使館法》指定由UFWD控制的組織-中國和平統一促進會（NACPU）-作為中國的外國使團，就像我們8月份時指定孔子學院美國中心作為外國使團時所做的那樣。<br />\n<br />\n除了NACPU，UFWD，還有其他分支機構試圖在中國傳播北京的惡性影響。我們將停止參加美利堅合眾國政府與中華人民共和國政府之間，關於建立美中兩國促進州際合作的州長論壇的諒解備忘錄，該備忘錄於2011年1月19日簽署。諒解備忘錄支持建立中美兩國州長論壇。然而，在諒解備忘錄簽署之後，總部設在北京、與地方政府聯手成立的中國人民對外友好協會（CPAFFC），一直試圖直接影響美國各州和地方的領導人，以促進中國的全球發展議程。 CPAFFC的行動破壞了這一論壇的初衷。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，真正的人與人之間的交流對於建立文化之間的理解至關重要，但UFWD並不是人與人之間交流的工具。取而代之的是，它使用諸如NACPU之類的組織來推進中國的宣傳和惡劣影響。今天的行動使我們在與中國建立透明和對等關係上邁進了一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/12-10282020171330.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2F12-10282020171330.html&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KivlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=50c9109e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/12-10282020171330.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e1a41050bb82bc9abf88ffbb0cbb58012fa4c5a","tid":2262087,"uid":4243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3584afbe3d4e3b2beffa4cbb64f288e0fd4391b2","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc81aa8c05cf270174ad427db5588a4fc4e6a0c4","tid":2262087,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:01:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">大和田立即坐返低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiUEX6S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiUEX6S.gif&h=23f74a11&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:26:52.000Z","msg":"西門點解你變到咁香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f62f9f84d8d9f1718e5e940543c9442723e9ec7","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1a41050bb82bc9abf88ffbb0cbb58012fa4c5a","tid":2262087,"uid":4243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3584afbe3d4e3b2beffa4cbb64f288e0fd4391b2","tid":2262087,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc81aa8c05cf270174ad427db5588a4fc4e6a0c4","tid":2262087,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:01:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">大和田立即坐返低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FiUEX6S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg